  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/SystemConfiguration\/kSCNetworkInterfaceIPv4\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T22:07:41Z\n---\n\n# kSCNetworkInterfaceIPv4\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nA network interface that can used for layering other interfaces (for example, 6to4, PPTP, or L2TP) over an existing IPv4 network.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet kSCNetworkInterfaceIPv4: SCNetworkInterface\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceType6to4**: The 6to4 interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeBluetooth**: The Bluetooth interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeBond**: The Ethernet bond interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeEthernet**: The Ethernet interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeFireWire**: The FireWire interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeIEEE80211**: The IEEE 802.11 interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeIPSec**: The IPSec interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeIrDA**: The IrDA interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeL2TP**: The L2TP interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeModem**: The modem interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypePPP**: The PPP interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypePPTP**: The PPTP interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeSerial**: The serial interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeVLAN**: The VLAN interface.\n- **kSCNetworkInterfaceTypeWWAN**: The WWAN interface.\n\n",
